 as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":759,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/06\/knowledge-death-scholars\/","url_meta":{"origin":6022,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Scholars: Knowledge disappears with death of &#8216;Ulama","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cVerily, Allah does not withhold knowledge by snatching it away from his servants, but rather he withholds knowledge by taking the souls of scholars, until no scholar remains and people follow ignorant leaders. They are asked and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25687,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/29\/angels-pray-with-him\/","url_meta":{"origin":6022,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Angels pray with one who prays alone","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farsi reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf a man is in a deserted land and the time of prayer arrives, let him perform ablution. If he does not find water, let him perform dry ablution. If he performs the prayer, two angels\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https: